OL,3,CMenai Supension Bridge: Weight limit
OL,4,Cintroduced
OL,6,FThe Menai Suspension Bridge has
OL,7,Fintroduced a weight limit of three
OL,8,Ftons with immediate effect.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government has said large
OL,11,Fvehicles will not be able to cross
OL,12,Fwith police in attendance to ensure
OL,13,Fcompliance.
OL,15,FThe limit has been recommended by
OL,16,Fengineers and described as urgent by
OL,17,Fthe Cabinet Secretary for Transport.
OL,19,FIt follows significant maintenance and
OL,20,Fupgrades to the bridge earlier this
OL,21,Fyear.
