OL,3,CMenai Supension Bridge: Weight limit
OL,4,Cintroduced
OL,6,FThe bridge is a significant structure
OL,7,Fproviding a vital crossing point
OL,8,Fbetween Ynys Mon and the mainland.
OL,10,FCars and heavy goods vehicles often
OL,11,Fuse the bridge to travel to Holyhead
OL,12,FPort, the second busiest port in the
OL,13,FUK.
OL,15,FThe limit is expected to cause
OL,16,Fsignificant disruption.
OL,18,FThe decision was made when an
OL,19,Finvestigation of the maintenance works
OL,20,Ffound some bolts on beams needed
OL,21,Freplacement.
