OL,3,CMenai Supension Bridge: Weight limit
OL,4,Cintroduced
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Cabinet Secretary
OL,7,Ffor Transport and North Wales, Ken
OL,8,FSkates said: "This is not a position
OL,9,Fwe would want to be in, but we must
OL,10,Flisten to the advice of engineers.
OL,12,F"I know this will cause particular
OL,13,Fconcern this evening with the arrival
OL,14,Fof Storm Amy and the potential impact
OL,15,Fthis may have on the Britannia Bridge.
OL,17,F"There are arrangements in place for
OL,18,Femergency vehicles to cross should the
OL,19,FBritannia be closed due to high winds.
